  type              General;
  benefit
  "Choose one of the creature’s natural attack forms. The
  damage for this natural weapon increases by one step, as if the
  creature’s size had increased by one category: 1d2, 1d3, 1d4, 1d6,
  1d8, 2d6, 3d6, 4d6, 6d6, 8d6, 12d6. A weapon or attack that deals
  1d10 points of damage increases as follows: 1d10, 2d8, 3d8, 4d8,
  6d8, 8d8, 12d8.";
  prerequisites
  "Natural weapon, base attack bonus +4.";
  worlds            Generic;
  references        WTC 17755: 304;
  description
  "The creature’s natural attacks are more dangerous than its size and
  type would otherwise dictate.";
  short description "Natural attacks do more damage.".

